IRON VALLEY REAL ESTATE NORTH FLORIDA

data.description: This STUNNING, WELL-MAINTAINED home is nestled in the heart of Yulee. Beautifully upgraded with Bianco Antico granite countertops, wood-look tile floors in main rooms, and plush carpet in the bedrooms, this spacious and open home is perfect for all your gatherings. Two sheds offer plenty of extra storage space, and the detached carport provides a shelter for your golf cart or additional vehicle. The fully fenced back yard is a safe space to play for children and pets. Flex room can easily convert to a 4th bedroom! Walk or a ride your bike to the NEW Nassau Crossing park, splash pad, and dog park! New HVAC in 2013, new exterior paint and stucco refurbishment in 2023, new water softener in 2022, new hot water heater in 2018, shallow well for irrigation to save on water costs. Convenient to Wildlight shopping and restaurants, I-95, and new medical facilities. Only a short drive from Kings Bay, Jacksonville, and Amelia Island.
